                    discardInput() // This is what ZLineEdit does as soon as new value is set
                    // We have no unit tests yet but setting values sin/cos=0 are of interest - so test
                    // cos: test with +10Â°/-10Â° and set cos=0. Expected 90Â°/-90Â°
                    // cos: test with +190Â°/170Â° and set cos=0. Expected 270Â°/90Â°
                    // sin: test with +80Â°/100Â° and set sin=0. Expected 0Â°/180Â°
                    // sin: test with +260Â°/280Â° and set sin=0. Expected 180Â°/0Â°
